data.description: Here is your opportunity to own a 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom, 2165 square foot pool home in Melrose Park that needs a little TLC. This home has NO carpet and ceramic tile throughout. The living room and family room offer great spots to entertain and are open to the kitchen. The master bedroom and master bathroom are not permitted. The master bathroom was just recently updated. The 3rd guest bathroom needs the shower finished. The backyard is your tropical oasis. It is fully fenced. You have an outdoor kitchen that needs some updating, inground pool, and a covered patio to entertain. This home is perfect for a family or an investor looking for his or her next rental home. The roof is 2014. The AC is 2014. Water heater is 2022. In a X flood zone, meaning NO flood insurance is required. Central location min from downtown Ft Lauderdale, i95 and turnpike. Come check out this home today, before it is gone tomorrow.
